<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Cadastro Newsletter</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .content { background: #fff; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px; }
        .field { margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .field strong { display: inline-block; width: 150px; color: #555; }
        .footer { margin-top: 20px; padding: 15px; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>üìß Novo Cadastro Newsletter</h2>
            <p>Um visitante se cadastrou para receber nossa newsletter.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h3>Dados do Cadastro:</h3>
            
            <div class="field">
                <strong>E-mail:</strong> {{ data.iEmail|default('N√£o informado') }}
            </div>
            
            {% if data.iName %}
            <div class="field">
                <strong>Nome:</strong> {{ data.iName }}
            </div>
            {% endif %}

            {% if data.iMsg %}
            <div class="field">
                <strong>Mensagem:</strong><br>
                {{ data.iMsg|nl2br }}
            </div>
            {% endif %}
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Informa√ß√µes do Sistema:</strong></p>
            <p>
                Lead ID: {{ lead_id|default('N/A') }}<br>
                Data/Hora: {{ "now"|date("d/m/Y H:i:s") }}<br>
                Tipo de Formul√°rio: {{ form_type|default('newsletter') }}<br>
                Sistema de Capta√ß√£o de Leads - Indemepreendimentos
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>